00:26:36,350 --> 00:26:37,340
I'm not doing it.

585
00:26:39,460 --> 00:26:41,700
Lord of All issues a quest.

586
00:26:43,260 --> 00:26:46,500
To celebrate the official proposal
to For Thy Sake,

587
00:26:47,500 --> 00:26:49,900
any friends who get married this month

588
00:26:50,100 --> 00:26:51,480
and present a wedding invitation

589
00:26:51,900 --> 00:26:53,140
will receive

590
00:26:53,380 --> 00:26:54,580
200 gold each.

591
00:26:57,940 --> 00:26:59,260
Isn't Lord of All

592
00:26:59,260 --> 00:27:01,300
already married to For Thy Sake?

593
00:27:01,300 --> 00:27:02,620
That was just in the game.

594
00:27:03,180 --> 00:27:04,860
I just heard from Tianxia Gang

595
00:27:05,100 --> 00:27:05,940
that they have

596
00:27:05,940 --> 00:27:08,300
actually gotten engaged in real life.

597
00:27:10,260 --> 00:27:11,180
Ace really nailed it.

598
00:27:12,270 --> 00:27:13,660
An online romance that turned real.

599
00:27:13,940 --> 00:27:14,780
Impressive.

600
00:27:15,380 --> 00:27:17,700
(Quest from Lord of All)
The Ace is so romantic.

601
00:27:18,620 --> 00:27:20,140
Setting such a high bar.

602
00:27:20,660 --> 00:27:22,980
I'll probably never get married.

603
00:27:27,700 --> 00:27:28,540
Jiang Anlan,

604
00:27:30,380 --> 00:27:31,820
looks like you really beat me.

605
00:27:36,980 --> 00:27:38,220
For real?

606
00:27:38,220 --> 00:27:39,780
Of course.

607
00:27:40,960 --> 00:27:42,890
Something this big can't be a joke.

608
00:27:48,140 --> 00:27:49,020
Boss.

609
00:27:49,020 --> 00:27:49,860
Morning.

610
00:27:50,740 --> 00:27:51,700
Master.

611
00:27:51,700 --> 00:27:53,040
Are you really getting married?

612
00:27:53,500 --> 00:27:55,100
Are you marrying Miss Yao?

613
00:27:55,860 --> 00:27:57,380
He's wearing a wedding ring.

614
00:27:57,380 --> 00:27:58,580
Do you think it's true?

615
00:28:03,060 --> 00:28:03,900
Jiang.

616
00:28:04,260 --> 00:28:05,780
I heard she said yes.

617
00:28:07,100 --> 00:28:08,860
If you want to congratulate me, go ahead.

618
00:28:12,940 --> 00:28:13,780
Jiang,

619
00:28:14,020 --> 00:28:14,860
let me ask you.

620
00:28:15,020 --> 00:28:15,940
Is it really right

621
00:28:16,260 --> 00:28:17,100
to marry her now?

622
00:28:19,860 --> 00:28:20,700
What's wrong with it?

623
00:28:22,190 --> 00:28:23,420
Your dad hasn't accepted her.

624
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:25,360
Marrying her under these circumstances,

625
00:28:25,780 --> 00:28:27,110
do you think it's good for her?

626
00:28:29,620 --> 00:28:31,300
I'm not sure if this is the best decision

627
00:28:31,300 --> 00:28:32,660
for Yao Yuan.

628
00:28:33,420 --> 00:28:34,540
But for me,

629
00:28:35,420 --> 00:28:37,300
it's unquestionable.

630
00:28:38,500 --> 00:28:39,980
I hope you treat her right.

631
00:28:40,220 --> 00:28:41,060
If not...

632
00:28:42,380 --> 00:28:44,060
There won't be an "if not."

633
00:28:47,140 --> 00:28:48,900
I hope you remember what you said.

634
00:28:50,740 --> 00:28:51,580
I will.

635
00:28:52,900 --> 00:28:53,740
So,

636
00:28:54,460 --> 00:28:56,100
would you take our wedding photos?

637
00:28:56,980 --> 00:28:58,620
That's a pretty cruel.

638
00:28:59,580 --> 00:29:00,420
But I will.

639
00:29:01,540 --> 00:29:02,380
For Yao Yuan.

640
00:29:25,820 --> 00:29:26,660
I feel so sad.

641
00:29:28,740 --> 00:29:30,180
Since last night,

642
00:29:30,980 --> 00:29:33,260
everyone in Shengshi has been celebrating

643
00:29:33,260 --> 00:29:35,420
Anlan's proposal to Yao.

644
00:29:38,620 --> 00:29:39,980
I really hate it.

645
00:29:41,620 --> 00:29:42,900
I don't hate Yao.

646
00:29:45,260 --> 00:29:47,060
I just hate this feeling.

647
00:29:47,420 --> 00:29:50,560
♪Love blooms like fireworks in the sky♪

648
00:29:51,330 --> 00:29:54,470
♪Soaring way up high, brightly♪

649
00:29:54,540 --> 00:29:56,050
I just feel really upset.

650
00:29:56,050 --> 00:29:58,320
♪Even if one day♪

651
00:29:58,850 --> 00:30:02,400
♪It'll fall down♪

652
00:30:02,740 --> 00:30:03,580
It's okay.

653
00:30:04,940 --> 00:30:05,930
Things will get better.

654
00:30:06,040 --> 00:30:12,150
♪That day, we walked side by side
down the street♪

655
00:30:12,180 --> 00:30:13,020
Why, really?

656
00:30:13,700 --> 00:30:15,420
Why doesn't Anlan like me?

657
00:30:16,580 --> 00:30:18,220
Am I really that bad?

658
00:30:20,980 --> 00:30:21,820
Of course not.

659
00:30:23,460 --> 00:30:25,660
Jianing, you're the best girl in the world.

660
00:30:25,660 --> 00:30:33,830
♪Someday, if you remember me
even for a moment♪

661
00:30:36,780 --> 00:30:37,620
You're really kind.

662
00:30:39,300 --> 00:30:41,490
I wish I liked you instead.

663
00:30:43,740 --> 00:30:44,580
Why can't you?

664
00:30:50,420 --> 00:30:51,260
Jianing.

665
00:30:52,900 --> 00:30:53,740
I hope that

666
00:30:56,180 --> 00:30:57,580
you could like me the way

667
00:30:58,540 --> 00:30:59,380
you like Anlan.

668
00:31:02,100 --> 00:31:05,740
Like you the way I like Anlan?

669
00:31:07,830 --> 00:31:10,750
♪Spreads the fragrance of summer♪

670
00:31:10,820 --> 00:31:12,100
Ancheng...

671
00:31:12,100 --> 00:31:12,940
I like you.

672
00:31:15,740 --> 00:31:17,100
Not like a brother to a sister.

673
00:31:19,300 --> 00:31:20,140
Do you understand?

674
00:31:22,220 --> 00:31:26,500
♪Yet behind a wall♪

675
00:31:27,280 --> 00:31:29,830
♪In a space without you♪

676
00:31:29,860 --> 00:31:31,700
But I've always seen you as my brother.

677
00:31:32,380 --> 00:31:34,020
I never thought it that way.

678
00:31:37,380 --> 00:31:38,220
It's okay.

679
00:31:40,060 --> 00:31:41,100
Take your time.

680
00:31:43,660 --> 00:31:44,620
I just hope I can

681
00:31:45,540 --> 00:31:46,520
mean more to you.

682
00:31:46,620 --> 00:31:54,990
♪That day, your smiling face
lit up the world♪

683
00:31:56,120 --> 00:32:04,020
♪Someday, if you remember me
even for a moment♪

684
00:32:04,380 --> 00:32:05,340
Mrs. Jiang,

685
00:32:05,340 --> 00:32:06,190
if you need flowers,

686
00:32:06,200 --> 00:32:07,860
just ask the gardener to pick some for you.

687
00:32:08,500 --> 00:32:10,420
Flowers you pick yourself always look better.

688
00:32:11,340 --> 00:32:12,380
You know me,

689
00:32:12,380 --> 00:32:14,260
I just love flowers.

690
00:32:18,820 --> 00:32:20,060
Hey, Jianing's here.

691
00:32:20,540 --> 00:32:21,460
Jianing,

692
00:32:21,460 --> 00:32:23,100
what's up?

693
00:32:23,100 --> 00:32:24,060
Did someone bother you?

694
00:32:30,140 --> 00:32:32,100
Anlan is getting married.

695
00:32:32,620 --> 00:32:33,460
What?

696
00:32:35,580 --> 00:32:36,500
Jianing.

697
00:32:36,500 --> 00:32:37,780
Don't speak nonsense.

698
00:32:38,860 --> 00:32:39,980
It's true.

699
00:32:40,740 --> 00:32:43,180
Anlan already proposed to Yao.

700
00:32:43,660 --> 00:32:45,020
Everyone knows about it.

701
00:32:46,220 --> 00:32:47,060
Auntie,

702
00:32:48,020 --> 00:32:49,380
I don't stand a chance now.

703
00:32:51,220 --> 00:32:52,780
It's way too soon to say that.

704
00:32:53,100 --> 00:32:55,020
He needs the family's approval to marry.

705
00:32:56,140 --> 00:32:56,980
Jianing,

706
00:32:57,180 --> 00:32:59,380
I think you and Anlan are the perfect match.

707
00:32:59,660 --> 00:33:01,060
Both in family background and looks,

708
00:33:01,260 --> 00:33:02,380
you're both top-notch.

709
00:33:04,780 --> 00:33:07,340
But Anlan likes Yao.

710
00:33:07,900 --> 00:33:09,660
No matter how hard I try.

711
00:33:12,460 --> 00:33:13,300
I think

712
00:33:13,940 --> 00:33:16,260
she must be coveting our wealth.

713
00:33:16,260 --> 00:33:17,940
That's why she came up with this scheme.

714
00:33:19,020 --> 00:33:19,940
Mrs. Jiang,

715
00:33:19,940 --> 00:33:21,420
you must not go soft on her this time.

716
00:33:23,620 --> 00:33:25,540
Auntie, please don't say that about Yao.

717
00:33:28,140 --> 00:33:30,420
Anlan hasn't told me about this.

718
00:33:30,940 --> 00:33:32,060
Don't jump to conclusions.

719
00:33:32,060 --> 00:33:33,420
Let me get the full story first.

720
00:33:41,260 --> 00:33:44,140
(Introduce her to family)

721
00:33:44,140 --> 00:33:47,100
(Propose to her)

722
00:34:07,860 --> 00:34:10,020
I'll be all alone at home from now on.

723
00:34:11,700 --> 00:34:12,540
That's perfect.

724
00:34:12,980 --> 00:34:15,060
You always say Yao Yuan is tone-deaf.

725
00:34:15,340 --> 00:34:16,700
Now it'll be quiet.

726
00:34:16,940 --> 00:34:18,380
I never said I liked quiet.

727
00:34:20,380 --> 00:34:23,060
I'll come over often to keep you company.

728
00:34:23,660 --> 00:34:24,500
Or,

729
00:34:26,060 --> 00:34:27,100
I can just move in.

730
00:34:27,100 --> 00:34:27,960
Forget it.

731
00:34:27,970 --> 00:34:29,260
Your life is a mess.

732
00:34:29,260 --> 00:34:30,610
You don't wash clothes or dishes.

733
00:34:30,700 --> 00:34:31,940
I'd rather live alone.

734
00:34:34,660 --> 00:34:36,700
Yuan has worked hard all these years.

735
00:34:37,260 --> 00:34:38,800
Finally, someone is taking care of her.

736
00:34:39,900 --> 00:34:40,940
But…

737
00:34:41,820 --> 00:34:42,660
But what?

738
00:34:43,340 --> 00:34:45,060
Although Anlan treats her well,

739
00:34:45,500 --> 00:34:46,740
I'm still worried.

740
00:34:47,700 --> 00:34:48,540
Worried about what?

741
00:34:48,850 --> 00:34:50,350
That she'll have too much money?

742
00:34:50,660 --> 00:34:51,500
I can help with that.

743
00:34:51,860 --> 00:34:53,260
You're too superficial.

744
00:34:54,140 --> 00:34:56,780
I heard Anlan's aunt is very bossy.

745
00:34:56,780 --> 00:34:58,900
I'm worried Yuan might have a hard time.

746
00:35:00,020 --> 00:35:01,500
Come on, Xinran.

747
00:35:01,500 --> 00:35:02,700
Don't overthink it.

748
00:35:03,180 --> 00:35:04,740
How could the Ace let her?

749
00:35:05,300 --> 00:35:07,460
But he can't be with Yuan 24/7.

750
00:35:07,860 --> 00:35:09,420
Dating is something between two people.

751
00:35:09,420 --> 00:35:11,380
After marriage, it's about two families.

752
00:35:12,580 --> 00:35:14,140
You know what she's like.

753
00:35:15,820 --> 00:35:18,540
That's why I'm so worried.

754
00:35:18,740 --> 00:35:19,980
She hates troubling others

755
00:35:19,980 --> 00:35:21,340
and takes on everything by herself.

756
00:35:21,340 --> 00:35:22,860
Even hurt, she says nothing.

757
00:35:24,100 --> 00:35:24,940
You're wrong.

758
00:35:25,460 --> 00:35:26,300
In my opinion,

759
00:35:26,460 --> 00:35:28,220
Yao Yuan has been through a lot.

760
00:35:28,820 --> 00:35:30,580
She looks quiet on the outside,

761
00:35:31,020 --> 00:35:33,100
but inside she's stronger than anyone.

762
00:35:33,820 --> 00:35:35,660
Even if she struggles in that family,

763
00:35:36,260 --> 00:35:37,460
she'll overcome it.

764
00:35:38,020 --> 00:35:39,180
And Yao Yuan is so likable,

765
00:35:39,720 --> 00:35:40,810
who'd give her a hard time?

766
00:35:41,140 --> 00:35:42,580
They will like her.

767
00:35:43,940 --> 00:35:46,100
So weird hearing you say that.

768
00:35:48,460 --> 00:35:49,700
I'm just brilliantly stupid.

769
00:35:50,300 --> 00:35:51,580
Yao Yuan is really resilient.

770
00:35:52,100 --> 00:35:53,060
You have to trust her.

771
00:35:53,060 --> 00:35:53,900
Alright.

772
00:35:53,910 --> 00:35:55,260
Here's to brilliantly stupid.

773
00:36:03,260 --> 00:36:04,100
Hey,

774
00:36:04,820 --> 00:36:06,220
isn't it inspiring that Yao Yuan

775
00:36:06,780 --> 00:36:08,180
is marrying the Ace?

776
00:36:08,740 --> 00:36:11,460
It shows a perfect match isn't just a dream.

777
00:36:11,980 --> 00:36:12,940
Maybe

778
00:36:12,940 --> 00:36:14,740
I might become her sister-in-law one day.

779
00:36:15,020 --> 00:36:15,860
Xiaoya,

780
00:36:18,100 --> 00:36:20,460
you're not seeing Li Ao, are you?

781
00:36:20,660 --> 00:36:21,500
Please.

782
00:36:21,860 --> 00:36:23,980
We got nothing going on, okay?

783
00:36:24,220 --> 00:36:25,700
Not a chance.

784
00:36:26,140 --> 00:36:28,580
Is it that rich playboy from your class?

785
00:36:29,340 --> 00:36:30,700
He's not rich at all.

786
00:36:30,900 --> 00:36:32,300
A total knockoff.

787
00:36:32,900 --> 00:36:34,220
Good thing Jiang Ancheng saved me.

788
00:36:34,220 --> 00:36:35,060
What?

789
00:36:35,540 --> 00:36:36,820
Jiang Ancheng?

790
00:36:38,220 --> 00:36:39,060
No.

791
00:36:39,220 --> 00:36:40,300
You heard wrong.

792
00:36:40,500 --> 00:36:41,740
Drink more. I'm off.

793
00:36:43,140 --> 00:36:44,100
See you tomorrow.

794
00:36:44,900 --> 00:36:45,740
Bye.

795
00:36:46,560 --> 00:36:48,940
How... how could it be Jiang Ancheng?

796
00:37:02,220 --> 00:37:03,060
Hey.

797
00:37:03,420 --> 00:37:05,230
Looks like you didn't sleep well last night.

798
00:37:05,980 --> 00:37:07,580
Sad about Master's getting married?

799
00:37:10,140 --> 00:37:11,420
Don't feel like talking.

800
00:37:17,580 --> 00:37:18,420
Come on.

801
00:37:18,980 --> 00:37:21,270
Yao getting married. I'm upset too.

802
00:37:21,730 --> 00:37:23,000
But I just slept it off.

803
00:37:24,220 --> 00:37:25,580
Besides, you still have me.

804
00:37:25,970 --> 00:37:27,080
It's going to be alright.

805
00:37:27,780 --> 00:37:28,620
Why would I need you?

806
00:37:33,740 --> 00:37:36,020
Then go find your Ancheng.

807
00:37:38,060 --> 00:37:38,940
Don't mention him.

808
00:37:40,660 --> 00:37:41,500
What's wrong?

809
00:37:42,060 --> 00:37:42,900
He...

810
00:37:44,780 --> 00:37:46,140
He said he likes me.

811
00:37:48,460 --> 00:37:49,300
He finally said it.

812
00:37:50,780 --> 00:37:51,620
What does that mean?

813
00:37:54,220 --> 00:37:55,540
The whole world saw it.

814
00:37:56,100 --> 00:37:57,100
You didn't?

815
00:37:58,740 --> 00:38:00,340
I thought he saw me as a sister.

816
00:38:01,620 --> 00:38:03,220
No man treats a sister that well.

817
00:38:04,780 --> 00:38:05,620
What should I do?

818
00:38:07,340 --> 00:38:09,100
Just ask your heart.

819
00:38:09,740 --> 00:38:11,340
Ask yourself if you really like him.

820
00:38:12,590 --> 00:38:13,540
I...

821
00:38:16,660 --> 00:38:18,220
(Ancheng)

822
00:38:18,220 --> 00:38:19,060
What should I do?

823
00:38:19,420 --> 00:38:20,260
Pick up.

824
00:38:21,380 --> 00:38:22,220
Answer it.

825
00:38:23,380 --> 00:38:24,500
I'm not ready to decide yet.

826
00:38:36,140 --> 00:38:37,020
Baby,

827
00:38:37,020 --> 00:38:38,780
don't add so much tomato.

828
00:38:39,660 --> 00:38:40,740
Don't call me that.

829
00:38:40,740 --> 00:38:42,540
Sounds weird.

830
00:38:42,540 --> 00:38:43,620
You better get used to it.

831
00:38:44,060 --> 00:38:46,060
I'll be calling you that
for the rest of my life.

832
00:38:46,900 --> 00:38:47,740
Stop it.

833
00:38:49,380 --> 00:38:51,480
♪You suddenly come into my life♪

834
00:38:51,700 --> 00:38:53,470
♪Our destiny is written♪

835
00:38:54,900 --> 00:38:56,020
You didn't put the lid on.

836
00:38:56,020 --> 00:38:56,860
Wife.

837
00:38:56,860 --> 00:38:58,570
♪That out of everyone, I find you♪

838
00:38:58,790 --> 00:39:00,940
♪It gives me a sense of love's warning♪

839
00:39:01,660 --> 00:39:03,260
Oh my god, what am I doing?

840
00:39:03,820 --> 00:39:04,660
What am I gonna do?

841
00:39:05,100 --> 00:39:06,260
I didn't bring any clothes.

842
00:39:07,990 --> 00:39:10,180
♪I'm starting to embrace this bond♪

843
00:39:10,190 --> 00:39:11,220
Go take a shower.

844
00:39:11,350 --> 00:39:12,690
I've prepared everything for you.

845
00:39:13,140 --> 00:39:14,460
You prepared my clothes?

846
00:39:14,740 --> 00:39:15,580
Mm.

847
00:39:15,580 --> 00:39:17,790
♪I don't ask for too much♪

848
00:39:17,790 --> 00:39:19,740
♪As long as you're my one and only♪

849
00:39:19,740 --> 00:39:20,900
(For my dear)

850
00:39:21,450 --> 00:39:25,130
♪My answer is just you and me♪

851
00:39:25,130 --> 00:39:27,470
♪Meeting you at the right time♪

852
00:39:27,470 --> 00:39:29,880
♪No matter how many dangers arise♪

853
00:39:30,700 --> 00:39:32,220
How did you know I use these?

854
00:39:32,660 --> 00:39:33,580
When you like someone,

855
00:39:33,580 --> 00:39:35,340
you have to know the details.

856
00:39:36,940 --> 00:39:38,700
You sure know way too much.

857
00:39:40,820 --> 00:39:41,700
Go take a shower.

858
00:39:42,140 --> 00:39:43,420
Your clothes are in the closet.

859
00:39:43,700 --> 00:39:45,940
I'll go be the family guy

860
00:39:45,940 --> 00:39:47,140
and clean up the mess.

861
00:39:47,140 --> 00:39:49,140
♪Forever heart♪

862
00:39:49,340 --> 00:39:50,860
Aren't you afraid of spoiling me?

863
00:39:51,060 --> 00:39:51,900
I'm not.

864
00:39:52,060 --> 00:39:53,300
You should be the one worried.

865
00:39:53,700 --> 00:39:55,260
I just want to spoil you so much

866
00:39:55,260 --> 00:39:56,260
that you can't leave me.

867
00:39:56,860 --> 00:39:57,980
I don't buy that.

868
00:39:58,340 --> 00:39:59,640
